@startuml hand-off-session-architecture

title hand_off_session — 模块架构 (baton 接力 5 大块)

' 节点名用日常术语优先,内部 module 名 / 函数名 / LOC / commit / REVIEW 引用见 INDEX

package "入口" as L1 {
  [MCP 入口 + 入口拦截\n(deny external)] as Entry
}

package "tool 实现" as L2 {
  [hand_off facade\n(参数解析 + cwd 反查 + adopt loop)] as Handler
  [plan resolve 业务层\n(读 plan + 校验 + 构造 cold start prompt)] as Impl
  [adopt context block\n(注入接管的 team 列表到 spawn prompt)] as AdoptCtx
}

note bottom of L2
  L2 子模块拆分 (hand-off-session.ts:1-37 jsdoc 列 6 子模块):
  - **facade** (handler.ts 主入口)
  - **_deps** (内部依赖 wiring)
  - **cwd-resolver** (cwd 反查 + 双模式 cwd 默认值)
  - **team-adopt-coordinator** (adopt loop + swapLead 转角色)
  - **task-reassign-coordinator** (clear-team / preserve-team / skip 三态过继)
  - **handler-main** (串联 prepareAdopt → spawn → phase1.5 swapLead → runTaskReassignment)
end note

package "起新 session" as L3 {
  [spawn 控制器\n(handOffMode=true 跳防御 + 不写 spawn-link)] as Spawn
  [adapter + SDK 子进程\n(claude / codex)] as Adapter
}

package "baton 收尾" as L4 {
  [baton 收尾流程\n(phase 1 关 teammate + phase 2 归档 caller)] as Baton
}

package "持久层 + 联动" as L5 {
  [4 张数据表\n(会话 / 团队 / 任务)] as Repos
  [会话管理器 + 事件总线] as SM
  folder "plan 文件 + worktree" as Fs
}

' ─── 调用链 ───

Entry --> Handler : 通过白名单后进 facade
Handler --> Repos : 反查 caller cwd
Handler --> Impl : plan-driven 模式调 plan resolve
Impl --> Fs : 按 fallback 链找 plan 文件
Impl --> Handler : 返 plan 元数据 + cold start prompt

note right of Handler
  双模式分流 (plan-driven vs generic) 细节
  详 hand-off-session-flow / decision 图
end note

Handler --> Spawn : 起新 SDK session
Spawn --> Adapter : claude / codex adapter
Adapter --> SM : upsert 新 session + emit event

Handler --> AdoptCtx : (pre-spawn) adopt_teammates=true → prepareAdoptSnapshotAndPrompt 装 adopt block 注入 spawn prompt
Handler --> Repos : (post-spawn) adopt_teammates=true → phase 1.5 runPhase15AdoptSwapLeadLoop 转交 lead 角色
Handler --> Repos : runTaskReassignment 改 task ownership (clear / preserve / skip 三态)
note right of Repos
  实际调用顺序 (handler-main.ts:178-306):
  prepareAdoptSnapshotAndPrompt (pre-spawn)
    → spawn (handOffMode=true)
    → phase 1.5 runPhase15AdoptSwapLeadLoop (post-spawn swapLead)
    → runTaskReassignment (按 team_task_policy 三态过继)
  preserve-team warning 依赖 phase15Detail.adoptedTeamIds
end note

Handler --> Baton : runBatonCleanup
Baton --> SM : phase 1 关 teammate (excludeSessionIds={newSid})
Baton --> Repos : phase 2 归档 caller session
Baton --> Handler : 返 cleanup 结果
Handler --> Entry : ok({sessionId, archived, adopted, taskReassignment, ...})

' ─── 关键不变量 ───

note bottom of Spawn
  关键不变量:
  - handOffMode=true → 跳 spawn-guards 三道防御 + 永不写 spawn-link
  - hand-off 是平级接力 (不是派遣关系),SessionList 不挂 teammate badge
  - plan-driven + external worktree (worktree 不在 mainRepo 子树) →
    handler 自动把 mainRepo 加进 spawn args.extra_allow_write
    (claude-code workspace-write 沙盒额外 writable roots,新 session 能写 plan 文件)
end note

note bottom of Baton
  与 archive_plan 共享 baton 流程(同 helper)
  phase 1 跳过条件 (6 状态完整 enum, baton-cleanup.ts:166-174 + shutdown-teammates-on-baton.ts:147,179):
  - **null**(成功路径含 closed=[] 的 caller=lead 但 team 内无其他 active teammate)
  - **'adopt-keep-implicit'**(adopt_teammates=true → teammate 已转给 newSid; Phase 4 引入)
  - **'archive-caller-false-keep'**(archive_caller=false → caller 保活; CHANGELOG_169 F4 引入)
  - **'caller-not-lead'**(caller 不是 lead 含 external sentinel)
  - **'all-lead-teams-archived'**(caller 是 lead 但所有 team 已 archived; REVIEW_56 §F6 R2 修法)
  - **'phase-1-error'**(phase 1 内部 throw 兜底; REVIEW_56 §F6 Plan-Review Round 2 codex MED-3)
  失败兜底见 hand-off-session-state-machine 图
end note

@enduml
